text: Günther Göllner (born 21 June 1941) is a German ski jumper. He competed at the 1968 Winter Olympics and the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of West Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:People from Poddębice County
